1. *Čuo* sam o tom slučaju iz prve ruke. (I heard about this case firsthand.)
2. On je *čuo* o mojoj situaciji. (He heard about my situation.)
3. *Čula* sam da ćeš biti tu. (I heard that you will be here.)
4. On je *čuo* da je ona već udata. (He heard that she was already married.)
5. *Čuvala* sam svoje novčanike dobro. (I kept my wallets safe.)
6. *Čulim* da su oni seli u novi stan. (I heard that they moved to a new apartment.)